Instructions on building
------------------------

This application was written and tested on Linux.
The application can be built using the Makefile in the folder Simulation

Dependencies / Requirements
---------------------------
- Eigen 3
- C++11
- glm OpenGL Math (http://glm.g-truc.net; apt-get install libglm-dev)
- Freeglut
- GLEW 1.6
- GLSL 1.5
- OpenGL 3.0
